    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>AIRLINE TAKEOVER IN CHINA</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Craig S. Smith</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Smith, Craig S</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>China's biggest airline, Southern Airlines Co, announces its acquisition of Zhongyuan Airlines (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>China's biggest airline, the Southern Airlines Company, said its parent company would take over Zhongyuan Airlines, the first airline merger since the government called July 21 for an industry consolidation to deal with overlapping routes and half-empty planes.</p>
        <p>Craig S. Smith</p>
      </block>
